      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that makes way more sense. one more thing though, i was reading that blockages can mess up the readings big time. like if something gets stuck in the tube, what actually happens to the airspeed indicator? like if the pitot tube gets blocked but the static port stays clear, what does the gauge show?",
